The embedded IP->timezone table (ip-timezones.bin) is derived from:

  DB-IP.com "IP to City Lite" database
  https://db-ip.com/db/lite.php
  Licensed under Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0)
  https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

IP-range latitude/longitude from DB-IP are resolved to IANA timezone names with
tzf-rs and merged by timezone (see tools/gen-ip-timezones/). As CC BY 4.0
requires, products that ship this data must credit db-ip.com.
